narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Wonderful- don't think Group Dynamics will be taught again, but if it is, I learned an incredible amount from this course.
PLSC 471 is a good option for a student to prepare for their senior thesis and explore a topic of interest not offered in a class.
